      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior upholstery shows some fading and minor staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will eventually require attention to the suspension and a tune-up to return to peak performance. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind some cosmetic and mechanical character.",
