    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional vehicle maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. An uncompromising choice for the discerning driver seeking a truly pristine, investment-grade driving experience.",
