    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it\u2019s always sparkling. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
