      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip rear differential. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a complete VANOS bulletproofing. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec bushings and updated Bilstein dampers, while the exterior retains its original deep luster with perfect panel gaps and zero oxidation. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters show no compression or wear. A mechanically flawless, turn-key example for the purist collector.",
